Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一用力就会粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪烁着七色的光芒的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是只有握紧的部分才会硬实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑亮黑亮的泥丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然形状不规则
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这是自己手指的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是为了某天能变成美丽的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了成为世界上最美的泥丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\be3\c&H6FFCEF&\3c&H639C15&\pos(327,188)}第77话 「防灾演习」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗外是一望无际的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹着初夏暖洋洋的风晒太阳令人身体舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有夏天的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么有股焦味？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 这是演习 防灾演习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 别处在做防灾演习的样……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突发火灾 突发火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在假设在河床上突发火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的把火点上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛啊 你这么做很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小招 真快啊 你是第一个……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么假设啊 这根本是放火嘛 放火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 我把周围的草都剪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 已经做好了防止火势扩散的措施啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太大惊小怪了 招兵买马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你在么？村长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你一看到火灾就赶过来看这点值得称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这种情况下才要保持冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实火是很可怕的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们可以支配火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你能不能先从修女身上下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 修女也太宠他了啦 这可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点根本算不上是在宠……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}啊 肚子有些饿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 修女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女的曲奇最好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女你是喂食的母鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的事也太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然知道修女有扔诱饵的怪癖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那如果你也这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我会把你打成马蜂窝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也太狠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长对我有恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能快到沸点了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感谢你了啊 修女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还是加了矿物质的「好味水」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的圆盘也饱饱满满的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真体贴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 这算不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体贴过头了吧 而且多此一举啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说河童头上圆盘的水干涸了的话 就会变得和婴儿一样无力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\be3\c&H875DF3&\4c&HF9F0FF&\bord3\pos(345,156)\3c&HD0C1D5&}第78话 「团队合作」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离火太近了吗 要离远点不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外 我从以前开始一直在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 有事尽管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么修女只对村长用敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来也不是很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会傻乎乎地笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有会让修女用敬语的理由……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你是第一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今年也很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火这东西还真是有魄力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 你变软趴趴了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 糟了 糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是小招吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真的都来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是每年的惯例
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那现在开始到底要干吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是作为防灾训练的重点的传水桶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把装着荒川河水的水桶传递到火灾地点灭火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是以团队合作为核心的灭火方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于一个个都是我行我素的 桥下居民来说这是不可能做到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我要打头阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要打头阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的 小孩子排到后面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成年男子打头阵怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 成年男子而且没带面具的我 小白或者修女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 为什么没有我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你歧视妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 万一你着火可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我讨厌塑料烧焦的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:24.28,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\frz339.343\pos(693,414)\3c&HC9C9C9&}{\c&H6A6A6A&}不\N老\N不\N死\N的\N礼\N物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 我要是烤熟了那可是人间美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用逞强了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能就这样算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来打头阵 好了 大家排成一直线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听我的号子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30} 「どすこい」是日本相扑选手在比赛时会喊的口号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}先不管号子 大家都很有干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 或者说是因为村长号子叫的好?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙出乎意料真的靠的住……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫 好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆盘要干了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴呆到后面去!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样直面危险的村长真帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油村长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就把下一桶传过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像大家都很仰慕他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\be3\pos(255,205)\c&H6FFCEF&\3c&H639C15&}第79话 「桥下的村长」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛啊 好不容易传过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女你也是 别太惯他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先歇会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:07:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你怎么对他好成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然刚才说过有恩什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为那个需要做到这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不光是恩情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是被恐吓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风把火星吹到旁边了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 三不 三不规定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说话很费劲……吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 三不是避难的时候的口诀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 正确的应该是 不要推 不要跑 不要说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不该交给什么河童的 一开始就该……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长 你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给村长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能交给那种布偶装的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不只是因为恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长是极少数有着值得尊敬价值的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且比任何人都爱着这桥底下的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 水桶都没带
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:08:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的 妖怪绝技 河童盘中水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 村长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浇得好 村长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把碟子里的水泼出去……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杯具啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家对于村长太过于盲目崇拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\be3\pos(255,205)\c&H6FFCEF&\3c&H639C15&}第80话 「顿悟」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 荒川河中游附近的宽阔的河床
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工程如果委托我们公司的话……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市宫先生 这是行少爷这一周的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是变得一脸白痴相了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:10:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由 权利 归属 全都是属于有钱人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就让你知道凭你这点力量根本无法获得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着灰色西装的一群忙碌男人 来到了翠绿耀眼的河边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这看起来很突兀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群人在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 到下一个地点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你们在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在勘察地基
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是研究还是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是施工前考察
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近要好好整顿下 好像说要建成公园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去过下游吗 那边有网球场吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然……已经决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个项目好像是我们社长直接接洽的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪里的……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市宫集团 你应该也听说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核战爆发!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是核战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那第二局我就让你赢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有比核战更恐怖的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸打算把桥下面给买下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是豪爽的爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 是那种压力太大就会冲动消费的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不算是买
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是以很低的价钱提出开发申请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是我在这里的事情被他知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:11:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道他在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但爸爸是那种言出必行的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像挺怕你爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然怕他！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女如果了解他的话也会……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没读圣经给你听了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱汝之敌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛祖也说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}{\c&H070707&\3c&HF3F3F3&}宗\N教\N穿\N越\N了\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论有几人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.64,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\3c&H514534&\pos(225,34)\c&HCEB54C&}这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准这里的话都能一枪搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一……枪……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样想的话 对谁都可以温柔以待了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道平常看着别人脑袋里都想着这种事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\be3\pos(255,205)\c&H6FFCEF&\3c&H639C15&}第81话 「紧急情况」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然小招也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始打牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想耍赖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在悠哉些个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白现在的情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的开始着手整顿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就没法留在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:13:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸可能打算把我们全赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他作对也赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连警察和媒体也都站在老爸那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确媒体是有点……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小河童
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:09.59,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(273,256)\frz0.982}好\N可\N爱\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.13,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(611,262)\frz349.19}河\N童\N哇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.13,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(269,270)\frz359.955}看\N这\N边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"荒川的小河童帅哥"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就会跻身偶像明星之列啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么白日梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样我们的存在触犯了法律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果警察被叫来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光一个严重警告未必能了事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说应该不会被逮捕……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEDEDED&\pos(811,259)}拐\N骗\N少\N女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEDEDED&\pos(675,325)}非\N法\N持\N刀\N持\N枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEDEDED&\pos(180,225)}制\N造\N噪\N音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEDEDED&\pos(53,255)}违\N法\N逗\N留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个百分之百会被抓的人!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在给我赶紧滚回英国去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 招兵买马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就跟修女说过如何应付 这种状况的魔法咒语了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论被问及什么都回答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶普通日鱼啦(我不懂日语啦)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样回答的话基本上什么都能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是小学生吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是日本人确实很怕老外说这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\be3\pos(255,205)\c&H6FFCEF&\3c&H639C15&}第82话 「不用担心」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上头条了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要上八点新闻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小招 你果然是个好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不知道情况有多……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然不想让你爸爸知道你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但从刚才开始你不都一直在担心别人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还特地跑来告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为我本来就住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是为了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己的家还有我们都会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这种毫无根据的话……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他的话如此鼓舞人心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一颗悬着的心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像冷静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃点饼干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况我也有是根据才说这里会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就料到会有这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就在桥下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙果然不是一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设下了 妖术 河童结界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在桥墩的四角
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋下了用糠包着的黄瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又浇了点煮河童水……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下真的完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腌泡菜完工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\be3\pos(255,205)\c&H6FFCEF&\3c&H639C15&}第83话 「公务员」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸无论在什么时候无论去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会毫不犹豫地选择最短路径
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度也格外的快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河川占用地再度开发一事我也是昨天才听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我自己也查过相关的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我今天貌似去不了弥撒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是国土交通省的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来请您尽快搬离河川的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其速度快到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人措手不及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没见过做到这份上的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间还真不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地基勘察已经结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太快了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么时候开始动工？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是日程表
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动工虽然还早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你最好早点离开噢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么说都算是犯罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不想麻烦到警察吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国土交通省的人上门让我们搬走？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没听说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这两天……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘁 我竟然大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然应该在昨晚就把 "防入侵者陷阱"设置好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手上那个带刺的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在戒备什么侵入？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 怎么突然就变这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这是……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国土交通省的混蛋公务员们!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一向温文尔雅的小白竟然气成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是河床
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是被人从家里赶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是国土交通省
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是我的爸爸……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}那种事已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空做这事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如给我去画更多的白线呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干这些事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了容身之所 又增加了不少像我一样不幸的"小白"啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}わたら(小白):玩只走白线游戏的简称
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小……小白?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没玩过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs32}超出白线就会被女生讨厌的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"在我回家以前不要从白线内出来"那个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能承担责任的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就不要画啥白线啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是弃猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我分不清到底是轻还是重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\be3\c&H6FFCEF&\3c&H639C15&\pos(228,201)}第84话 「猪」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎么办呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}哥哥哥哥 到底该怎么办好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和碰到公务员的只有小招一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上大家都聚在这里做弥撒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有一个绝对不会来做弥撒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我是国土交通省的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这片河床到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然迄今为止还没上过头条
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从大清早开始就精力旺盛的 只要那个有女装癖的家伙一人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大美人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对对对不起 我是国土交通省的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 公务员吗 真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天稍微有点事情想请……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊 你说来听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个公仆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于要施工 所以那个搬迁……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公仆？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来求人的话 就应该有相应的态度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我感到荣幸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来教你这没规矩的臭虫该怎么说人话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不是公务员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家老实点什么都别做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看上去态度还蛮强硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会大发雷霆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是为国家做事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他惹毛了不知道会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 在下是国土交通省的 名叫铃木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是被人民养着的一头丑陋的猪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求各位国民……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这位先生……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 万分抱歉自己是一个没有教养的猪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里之前遇到了牧场的大姐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起对不起对不起……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}刚睡醒的玛利亚是S级的化身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}完全意料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\be3\pos(255,205)\c&H6FFCEF&\3c&H639C15&}第85话 「在这里」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是另外一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真的要施工了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是……是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还没投标
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但基本上已经定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想先告诉各位一声的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我这头猪就此告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:20:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的话真的就要从这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬走不就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在靠近水源的地方不也挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能说这么不负责任的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不愿意再被赶走 也不要再跟大家分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\be3\pos(255,205)\c&H6FFCEF&\3c&H639C15&}第86话 「荒川一击必杀预选」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇滚明星一击必杀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:22:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THE 即兴之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给一个词我就能即兴唱一段
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.51,0:23:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.96,0:23:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大麦茶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK~BABY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗耳恭听我的歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标题是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谨慎的我DVD最低三盘可以出租
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.71,0:23:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为有一个人可以猜中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.67,0:23:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到一个都没中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.55,0:23:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}(不合格 不合格 不合格 罢免)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 仔细一看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大麦茶的行星其实都是橘子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连那个章鱼的传说也是……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来咯～ 跟我一起唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Hey Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰它手指会被卷进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说着的小珊把什么东西揉成了团
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴里有什么爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.44,0:23:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊在喝碳酸饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.25,0:23:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难的算式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.46,0:23:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是汽车牌照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.76,0:23:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回 11桥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是和小珊的旁白对话
